quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Hɑɑ miim"
  44,2,"Ne gaf-vẽenegã."
  44,3,"Ad Tõnd sik-a-la yʋng pʋgẽ sẽn yaa bark yʋngo, ad Tõnd yɩɩme n yaa bugsdba."
  44,4,"Yʋʋn-kãngɑ pʋgẽ la b welgd yell buud fãa sẽn bʋ n manege."
  44,5,"Tɩ yaa sagls sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ, ad Tõnd yɩɩme n yaa Tʋmsdba."
  44,6,"Tɩ yaa yolsg sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ; ad Yẽnda la Wʋmd n ya Mita."
  44,7,"Yaa saasã lɑ tẽngã, la sẽn be b yiibã sʋk Soɑbã, yãmb sã n yaa bãng-n-wãak rãmba, bɩ y kõ sɩd ne Mɑm tẽn-tʋʋmã."
  44,8,"Soab ka be sẽn na n tũ n tɩlg tɩ pa Yẽ ye, A kʋʋdame la A vʋʋgdẽ, yaa yãmb Soaba, yaa y baaba-rãmb sẽn reng taoor me Soaba."
  44,9,"Pa woto ye, bãmb bee sik pʋgẽ n reemdẽ."
  44,10,"Bɩ f koll-ba, raar ning saagã sẽn na n wa n yaa wulwuku tɩ yɑɑ vẽenega."
  44,11,"N buiid fo nebã, lɑ b yet-bɑ, ad wãnde yaa namsg sẽn zabde,"
  44,12,"""D Soab a Wẽnde! Pãrg naongã n bas-do, ad tõnd yaa sɩd-kõtba"""
  44,13,"La tẽegr na n nafa bãmb wãn-wãna tɩ tẽn-tʋʋm sẽn yaa vẽeneg ra waa bãmb nengẽ!"
  44,14,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ bãmb gõd b zãn-kuids n bas-a la b yeele: "" yɑɑ karem-biig sẽn yaa gãeenga""."
  44,15,"Ad Tõnd na n pãrga naongã bilfu, ad y na n le lebame."
  44,16,"Raar ning sẽn na n wẽoog-b wẽoog kεgengã, ad Tõnd yaa sɩbgdba."
  44,17,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd zarba sẽn reng bãmb taoore, a Fɩr-aoon nebã, tɩ tẽn-tʋʋm wagell wa b nengẽ."
  44,18,"(n yeel-ba:) ""bas-y Wẽnd yembsã tɩ b wa mam nengẽ, tɩ mam yaa tẽn-tʋʋm sẽn yaa vẽeneg ne yãmba""."
  44,19,"La y ra zẽk y mens ne Wẽnd ye, ad mam na n waa ne daliil (vẽnegr) sẽn yaa vẽeneg yãmb nengẽ."
  44,20,"La ad mam kota gũudum ne m Soabã la yãmb Soabã, tɩ y ra wa lob-m ye."
  44,21,"La yãmb sã n ka kõ sɩd ne maam, bɩ y ball n bas-ma."
  44,22,"T'a na n bool a Soabã, (n yeele): ""bãmbã yaa nin-wẽnse"""
  44,23,"T'A yeele: ""yi ne M yembsã n bob yʋngo, ad b na n pʋga yãmba."""
  44,24,"La f bas mogrã hãoo tɩ ad b yaa tãp b sẽn na n bõr-b""."
  44,25,"Sõor waoog b sẽn bas sẽn yaa pʋt la ko-nin."
  44,26,"La kood la zags sẽn yaa wagla."
  44,27,"La neema-rãmb b sẽn da be beenẽ n wʋmsd noogo."
  44,28,"Yaa woto bala, la Tõnd rɩka b faadã n kõ neb a taaba."
  44,29,"La saag la tẽng pa kũm b yĩng ye, b pa yɩ me n ya b sẽn na n koll-b rãmb ye."
  44,30,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd tɩlga ɭsraεεl koambã n yi naon-yaandga."
  44,31,"N yi a Fɩr-aoona, ad a yɩɩme n yaa zẽk-m-meng soab maan-n-zʋʋk rãmbã pʋgẽ."
  44,32,"La ad Tõnd tũus-b lame, Tõnd minim pʋgẽ, bõn-nandsã fãa zugu."
  44,33,"La D kõ-b yel-soalem-rãmba, tɩ zarb-n-gɛsg sẽn ya vẽeneg sẽn be a pʋgẽ."
  44,34,"Ad bãmbã sẽn kɩɩsd Yikrã na yeele:"
  44,35,"""Ad vɩɩm kɑbe rẽndame tɩ yaa tõnd kũ-rãeengã bala, tõnd pa yɩ n yaa b sẽn na n yik-b rãmb ye."""
  44,36,"Bɩ y wa ne tõnd baaba-rãmbã tɩ y sã n yaa sɩd-rãmb."
  44,37,"La bãmb sõmblem n yɩɩd bɩ yaa Tʋba'ɑ nebã la sẽn reng-b bãmb taoorã? Tõnd halk-b lame, ad b yɩɩme n yaa wẽngdba."
  44,38,"La Tõnd pa naan saasã la tẽngã la sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã reem yĩng ye."
  44,39,"Tõnd pa naan b yiibã ralla ne sɩda, la ad b wʋsgã fãa pa mi ye."
  44,40,"Ad Welgrã Raar la b fãa kɛp sεka."
  44,41,"Raar ning lalld sẽn pa nafd a lall-n-taag ba fʋɩ, b pa tõe n song taaba."
  44,42,"Sã n pa Wẽnd sẽn yols-a soaba, ad Yẽnda la Wind n yaa Yolsda."
  44,43,"Ad (zakʋʋm) tok-sẽnegã tɩɩgã."
  44,44,"Yaa beegdb rɩɩbo."
  44,45,"A yaa wala zũud koom n kaeed pʋsẽ wã."
  44,46,"Wala ko-tʋʋlg kaeebo."
  44,47,"(Tɩ b yet bugumɑ mɑlεgsã):Yõk-y-yã-a n vẽs n kẽng Bugmã sʋka."
  44,48,"Rẽ poorẽ bɩ y kiig a zugã sʋk ko-tʋʋlgã."
  44,49,"Lembe, tɩ foo la zɩsg n yaa wagelle."
  44,50,"Ad yaa wãnde la yãmb sẽn maan sik ne wã."
  44,51,"Ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee bas-m-yam zĩigẽ."
  44,52,"Arzãn-rãmb pʋgẽ la ko-nini."
  44,53,"B yeelgd-b-la fu-faas la fu-taga, tɩ b yaa sẽn togl taaba."
  44,54,"Woto bal la D furd-b pʋg-neeb nin sẽn yaa yalemse ."
  44,55,"B boondame tɩ wat a pʋgẽ, sẽn yaa tɩ-biig buud fãa, tɩ b yaa bas-m-yam rãmba."
  44,56,"B pa lembd kũum a pʋgẽ, rẽnda kũ-rãeengã, tɩ b Soabã gũ-b n yi Bug-yõogdgã."
  44,57,"Tɩ yaa kũuni sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ, ad wãnde la pʋɩɩr sẽn yaa zɩsgo."
  44,58,"La ad Tõnd yols-a-la ne fo zɩlemdã, sãnd-sãnde b na tags n gese."
  44,59,"Bɩ f koll-ba, tɩ ad bãmb me yaa kolldba."
